15:45.400 --> 15:48.312
<i>Plawn clackers</i> and <i>minelal water.</i>

15:48.520 --> 15:50.112
There you go.
- Thanks.

15:50.440 --> 15:56.037
You can learn to live with it.
- Your colleague said that too.

15:56.240 --> 15:58.754
'In some cases people
just learn to live with it.'

15:58.960 --> 16:03.431
But what about the other cases?
- OK...

16:06.000 --> 16:08.594
