I won't carry on stumbling on.

18:22.000 --> 18:23.194
Meaning?

18:23.400 --> 18:26.278
I'm not going to die
a slow, painful death like my grandma.

18:26.480 --> 18:29.677
Let's not go on about
Dying With Dignity again.

18:29.880 --> 18:32.599
